BEGIN:VCALENDAR
VERSION:2.0
PRODID:-//The Finance Lab//College Project Student Calendar//EN
X-WR-CALNAME:College Project: Your Senior Year Deadlines
X-WR-CALDESC:Key California college and financial aid deadlines, with reminders. Repeats every year.
X-WR-TIMEZONE:America/Los_Angeles
CALSCALE:GREGORIAN
METHOD:PUBLISH
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-apps-open@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260801
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260802
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:📅 UC & CSU applications open
DESCRIPTION:You can start filling out your UC and CSU applications now. Build your college list (reach, match, safety).
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P2D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:UC & CSU applications open soon
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-rec-letters@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260915
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260916
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:📝 Ask teachers for letters of recommendation
DESCRIPTION:Ask early, while teachers still have time. Junior-year teachers are ideal. Give them your brag sheet.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P7D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Ask for rec letters this week
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-fafsa-open@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261001
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261002
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:💰 FAFSA & CA Dream Act open — file as early as you can
DESCRIPTION:The FAFSA and CA Dream Act Application (CADAA) both open October 1. Filing early means earlier aid offers. You need this for Cal Grant (deadline March 2).
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P2D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:FAFSA / CADAA opens in 2 days
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-ea-ed@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261101
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261102
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:📅 Early Action / Early Decision deadlines (many Nov 1–15)
DESCRIPTION:If you are applying early to private or out-of-state schools, those deadlines are usually Nov 1–15. Early Decision is binding, so know the financial risk first.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P7D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Early deadlines coming up
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-uc-csu-deadline@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261130
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261201
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:📅 UC & CSU application deadline — submit by today
DESCRIPTION:Both the UC and CSU applications are due November 30. Submit before the site gets slow on the last day.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P7D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:UC & CSU apps due in 1 week
END:VALARM
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P1D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:UC & CSU apps due TOMORROW
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-rd-deadline@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270101
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270102
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:📅 Regular Decision deadlines (many Jan 1–15)
DESCRIPTION:Most private and out-of-state Regular Decision applications are due January 1 or 15. Confirm each school's exact date.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P7D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Regular Decision deadlines this week
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-fa-priority@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270115
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270116
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:💰 Check each college's financial aid priority deadline
DESCRIPTION:Many colleges have their own financial aid priority deadlines in January and February. Complete the CSS Profile if a school requires it.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P7D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Check financial aid priority deadlines
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-cal-grant@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270302
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270303
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:💰 CAL GRANT DEADLINE — today (firm)
DESCRIPTION:To qualify for Cal Grant, your FAFSA or CADAA AND your school-certified GPA must be submitted by March 2. This deadline does not move.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P14D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Cal Grant deadline in 2 weeks — check your FAFSA & GPA
END:VALARM
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P2D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Cal Grant deadline in 2 days
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-decisions@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270401
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270402
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:📅 Decisions arrive — compare your aid offers
DESCRIPTION:Most schools notify by early April. Put your offers side by side: net price, grants vs loans, whether aid renews, total cost. Keep your head up if a no comes.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P1D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Decisions and aid offers arriving
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-decision-day@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270501
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270502
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:🎓 College Decision Day — submit your SIR & deposit
DESCRIPTION:May 1 is the national deadline to accept your offer. Submit your Statement of Intent to Register (SIR) and enrollment deposit. Cannot afford the deposit? Ask about a fee waiver.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P7D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Decision Day in 1 week
END:VALARM
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P1D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Decision Day is TOMORROW
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-final-transcript@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270610
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270611
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:🎓 Send your final transcript & sign up for orientation
DESCRIPTION:Most colleges require your final high school transcript before you can enroll. Ask your counselor to send it, then sign up for orientation and placement tests.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P2D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Send final transcript, sign up for orientation
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sr-summer-melt@thefinancelab.co
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270701
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270702
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:💰 Summer: check your portal & email every week
DESCRIPTION:Most students who get in but never start missed one summer email about aid, housing, or verification. Check weekly. If money gets scary, call the financial aid office, do not walk away.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P1D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Keep checking your college portal this summer
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
